Sec. 47.054. PROGRAM STAFF. (a) The commissioner shall employ
one or more persons as employees of the department to staff the
program.
(b) Unless otherwise expressly provided by the legislature, the
source of funding for the payment of employee salaries shall be funds
generated from the program, including the 10 percent license fee
increase authorized by Section 77.002, Parks and Wildlife Code.
Added by Acts 2003, 78th Leg., ch. 265, Sec. 6, eff. June 18, 2003;
Acts 2003, 78th Leg., ch. 677, Sec. 4, eff. June 20, 2003.
Amended by:
Acts 2009, 81st Leg., R.S., Ch. 1052 (H.B. 4593), Sec. 4, eff.
September 1, 2009.

